cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as edge detection, image classification, and image denoising. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also utilizes deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a multi-scale U-net architecture, which is a neural network architecture commonly used in image segmentation tasks, suggesting that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which could place it in the cs.MM (Multimedia) category.
